

IO-LUA is a 2D game engine for Lua.

Current platform support: Linux, Mac OS X, Windows

You can download the precompiled game engine:

Windows: http://abacus.subluminal.net/~jakashthree/io-lua%20windows.zip
Mac OS X: http://abacus.subluminal.net/~jakashthree/io-lua%20macosx.zip
Linux: http://abacus.subluminal.net/~jakashthree/io-lua%20linux.zip

Compiling for Linux or Mac OS X:
	make

Compiling for Windows (use Visual Studio Command Prompt):
	build.bat

See https://github.com/Protovision/io-lua/wiki for documentation
